rtical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 1em; word-break: break-word; clear: both; max-width: 100%; outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bolder;\">示例代码：</span>提供热门的API示例代码和典型场景示例。</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; word-break: break-word;\">下面就让我们来看看这三个子页面的具体功能：</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; word-break: break-word;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bolder;\">1. 原子化服务组件</span></p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; word-break: break-word;\">在&ldquo;原子化服务组件&rdquo;子页面，开发者可以按组件类型（比如UI、动画类、安全类等）或组件类型组合筛选出所需的组件，点击后即可进入该组件的详情页面。</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 1em; word-break: break-word; clear: both; color: #333333; letter-spacing: 0.544px; max-width: 100%; outline: 0px; text-align: justify;\">组件详情页面展示该组件的描述、与其他组件的依赖关系、安装命令等信息，并提供各版本（包括历史版本）的下载功能。</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 1em; word-break: break-word; clear: both; color: #333333; letter-spacing: 0.544px; max-width: 100%; outline: 0px; text-align: justify;\">从图6可以看到，对于动画类组件，&ldquo;描述&rdquo;中支持展示此组件的动画效果，并提供此组件的详细介绍、使用说明、配置说明等信息。</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-c