ing: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: none; word-break: break-word; background: transparent; outline: 0px;\"><img class=\"previewableImage\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: middle; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\" src=\"https://alliance-communityfile-drcn.dbankcdn.com/FileServer/getFile/cmtybbs/300/118/079/0890086000300118079.20210924115004.11271469605143285045181662492455:50520923065936:2800:577DAEC33748DD496FE29A5EB7C9305AA8852D4A3FF7A01EB9674F3BAE5EF819.png\" alt=\"图8.png\" /></span></p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 1em; word-break: break-word; clear: both; color: #333333; letter-spacing: 0.544px; max-width: 100%; outline: 0px; text-align: center;\">图8 工程模板</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 1em; word-break: break-word; clear: both; color: #333333; letter-spacing: 0.544px; max-width: 100%; outline: 0px; text-align: justify;\">了解过DevEco Studio 2.2 Beta2新版本功能的开发者，应该已经知道DevEco Studio新增了模板市场的功能。从DevEco Studio最新版本就能直接获取DevEco Marketplace网站上的工程模板啦！具体详情，请看我们之前的<span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bolder;\">DevEco Studio 2.2 Beta2</span>上新推文。</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 1em; word-break: break-word; clear: both; color: #333333; letter-spacing: 0.544px; max-width: 100%; outline: 0px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bolder;\">3. 示例代码</span></p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 1em; word-break: break-word; clear: both; color: #333333; letter-spacing: 0.544px; max-width: 100%; outline: 0px; text-align: justify;\">在&ldquo;示例代码&rdquo;子页面，开发者可以按类型（比如ability、common、device等）或类型组合筛选出所需的示例代码，点击后即可进入该示例代码详情页面。如图9所示，示例代码详情页面提供了该代码的详细介绍，并且支持点击&ldquo;仓库地址&rdquo;一键直达Gitee查看源码。</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 1em; word-break: break-word; clear: both; color: #333333; letter-spacing: 0.544px; max-width: 100%; outline: 0px; text-align: center;\"><span class=\"easyimage easyimage-full\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: none; word-break: break-word; background: transparent; outline: 0px;\"><img class=\"previewableImage\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: middle; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\" src=\"https://alliance-communityfile-drcn.dbankcdn.com/FileServer/getFile/cmtybbs/300/118/079/0890086000300118079.20210924115017.31284240778508149167340555764430:50520923065936:2800:1A38108A0DE8E9D19C93C7A7DC5B7F74FEEAB9EAC803BEA78ACF70C8D49BF1C6.png\" alt=\"图9.png\" /></span></p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 1em; word-break: break-word; clear: both; color: #333333; letter-spacing: 0.544px; max-width: 100%; outline: 0px; text-align: center;\">图9 示例代码</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 1em; word-break: break-word; clear: both; color: #333333; letter-spacing: 0.544px; max-width: 100%; outline: 0px; text-align: justify;\">除了以上资源库，DevEco Marketplace网站的&ldquo;贡献&rdquo;页面为开发者们提供了一个开发资源分享平台。欢迎开发者参与鸿蒙生态共建，将原创的组件、示例代码共享给开发者伙伴们使用。</p>\n我们始终以开发者的开发体验为先，持续输出助力高效开发的工具平台，只为服务每一个你。登录<a style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; background: 0px 0px transparent; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; transition: color 0.3s ease 0s; color: #0782c1; touch-action: manipulation; text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer;\" href=\"https://repo.harmonyos.com/\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"nofollow\">DevEco Marketplace（<span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; word-break: break-word; color: #328dff;\">https://repo.harmonyos.com/</span>）</a>试用吧！</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', '', 5, ',2,21,26,27,23,', '改进意见', '公开', '已发布', '精华', 0, '', '', 1, 0, '2022-04-23 23:27:58', '2022-04-24 00:04:05');
