box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bold; word-break: break-word;\">throw</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bold; word-break: break-word;\">new</span> RuntimeException(<span class=\"hljs-string\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #880000; word-break: break-word;\">\"Stub!\"</span>);\n    }\n</code><button style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 4px 8px 0px; touch-action: manipulation; font-size: 14px; font-family: inherit; line-height: inherit; overflow: visible; appearance: button; position: absolute; cursor: pointer; top: 4px; right: 8px;\">复制</button></pre>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; word-break: break-word; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">其中，AbilitySliceAnimator 除了 无参构造方法以外，</p>\n<ul style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 40px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\n<li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\">AbilitySliceAnimator(float fromX, float fromY, float toX, float toY) 传入四个参数，从（x,y）到（x,y）为坐标。</li>\n<li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\">setDuration(long duration)，该方法表示切换过程的&nbsp;<span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bolder;\">时长</span>，默认300 ms</li>\n<li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\">setDelay(long delay)，该方法表示推迟切换的&nbsp;<span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bolder;\">时长</span>。单位 ms</li>\n<li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\">setRepeatCount(int repeatCount) ，该方法表示重复播放切换动画的次数。&nbsp;<span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bolder;\">此时需注意，如果传入 1 ，表示重复 1 次，一共播放 2 次。如果传入 0 ，表示重复 0 次，一共播放 1 次。</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; word-break: break-word; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">知晓了以上知识，还有一点：怎么切换？X 和 Y 分别代表哪里？</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; word-break: break-word; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">举个例子：</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; word-break: break-word; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">页面的原点在左上角，（0，0），往右 x 增加，往下 y 增加。现在有两个 AbilitySlice，分别是 a 和 b ，默认显示的是 a ，现在切换到 b，默认 b 页面是从右边滑到左边，即页面是从（1080，0）到（0，0）。</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; word-break: break-word; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bolder;\">关注点需要始终在页面左上角！！</span>，如何从左边到右边呢？</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; word-break: break-word; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">换位思考一下，假设现在显示的是 b ，要返回 a，a 把 b 向左推，把 b 从 （0，0）推到了（-1080，0）。那么要显示 b ， b 从左边把 a 往 右边推，b 的坐标是从（-1080，0）到（0，0）.</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; word-break: break-word; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">这样就明白了为什么上面是从（-1080，0）到（0，0）。</p>\n<blockquote style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 2px 8px 2px 20px; vertical-align: baseline; border-width: 0px 0px 0px 5px; border-style: solid; border-color: #cccccc; border-image: initial; quotes: none; font-style: italic; font-family: Georgia, Times, \'Times New Roman\', serif; color: #2a2b31; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; word-break: break-word; min-height: 28.8px;\">至于，想让这个页面单独这样的...我暂未深入研究，可以让【想让他使用默认跳转动画】的页面，放到另一个 Ability 中。目前由于时间关系未深究，后续补充。知道的小伙伴可以分享呀~</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #333333; font-weight: 400; font-size: 24px; line-height: 1.2; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">2、如何关闭切换动画</h2>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; word-break: break-word; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">1、setTransitionAnimation(0,0); 这种方法。</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; word-break: break-word; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">在 startAbility(intent); 方法执行后再执行，取消两个Ability之间跳转动画：</p>\n<pre style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: couriernew, courier, monospace; overflow: auto; white-space: pre-wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; tab-size: 4; color: #2a2b31; background-color: #ffffff; position: relative;\"><code class=\"language-java hljs \" style=\"-