; border: 0px; color: #008800; word-break: break-word;\">1</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #008800; word-break: break-word;\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #008800; word-break: break-word;\">0</span>},<span class=\"hljs-comment\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #888888; word-break: break-word;\">//Exit</span>\n    };\n</code><button style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 4px 8px 0px; touch-action: manipulation; font-size: 14px; font-family: inherit; line-height: inherit; overflow: visible; appearance: button; position: absolute; cursor: pointer; top: 4px; right: 8px;\">复制</button></pre>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">小伙伴们可自行根据规则添加测试序列。</p>\n<h2 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #333333; font-weight: 400; font-size: 24px; line-height: 1.2; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">5. 发现并修复bug</h2>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">在写ledx测试程序做验证时，发现死活都得不到预期效果，我就干脆从下到上把整个流程画了图出来，发现驱动程序果然有不可预料的行为。</p>\n<h3 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #333333; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.2; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">5.1 LED灯的数量</h3>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">在没得到原理图和GPIO管脚编号的情况下，我猜测DAYU200开发板排线旁边的LED灯，应该是如下图所示：&nbsp;<img class=\"previewableImage\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: middle; border: 0px; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://alliance-communityfile-drcn.dbankcdn.com/FileServer/getFile/cmtybbs/427/913/123/2850086000427913123.20220419194151.33786470331544522890539188902856:50530422153932:2800:FA68DCE453D817D06A6B91A8F6FC13DF3906CDD3E1DF68AF982BC55D4E32BD1B.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">在light_config.hcs中写 lightId = [1, 2]; 相当于说是有两盏灯，但实际上，要么是1盏，要么是3盏，我这里暂且把RGB合在一起当做一盏灯来处理。【小伙伴们可尝试一下把它当做三盏灯来处理，看看该怎么改。】</p>\n<h3 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #333333; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.2; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">5.2 GpioWrite()的行为</h3>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">light_driver.c中对GpioWrite()的几处调用中，对drvData-&gt;info[lightId]-&gt;busNum的使用，很明显是不合理的，这是造成测试效果不符合预期的根本原因。 我对此做了一下修改，用 UpdateLight(uint32_t lightId, uint32_t lightOn)来替代，小伙伴们读一下附件的代码估计就清楚了。</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">【无法上传附件】 请到&nbsp;<a style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; background: 0px 0px transparent; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; transition: color 0.3s ease 0s; color: #0782c1; touch-action: manipulation; text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer;\" href=\"https://ost.51cto.com/posts/11566\">RK3568三色灯点灯流程/测试用例/修复bug</a>&nbsp;这里去下载测试程序和源代码。</p>', '', 13, ',67,63,71,70,', '翻译', '公开', '已发布', '', 0, '', '', 1, 0, '2022-04-23 23:40:02', '2022-04-24 00:02:52');
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES (18, '普适各类IoT场景，润和HH-SLNPT100开发板通过OpenHarmony兼容性测评', 3, '', '<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 1em; word-break: break-word; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; clear: both; max-width: 100%; outline: 0px; visibility: visible;\">近日，润和海王星系列HH-SLNPT100开发板顺利通过OpenHarmony 1.1.0 LTS 版本兼容性测评，获颁OpenAtom OpenHarmony（以下简称OpenHarmony）生态产品兼容性证书，成为继2021年8月9日首批通过兼容性测评的开发板&mdash;润和&ldquo;Hi3861 HiSpark开发板&rdquo;及2022年1月24日首个通过兼容性测评的软件发行版&mdash;&ldquo;HiHopeOS 1.0 RC1 IoT Edition&rdquo;之后，润和软件第三款获颁兼容性证书的OpenHarmony产品。至此，润和软件通过兼容性测评的生态产品已达三款，覆盖了软硬件双向的产品层级。</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 1em; word-break: break-word; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; clear: both; max-width: 100%; outline: 0px; visibility: visible;\"><span class=\"easyimage easyimage-align-left\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 1.5em 0px 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: none; word-break: break-word; background: transparent; outline: 0px; min-width: 10px;\"><img class=\"previewableImage\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: middle; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: 468px; width: 327px;\" src=\"https://alliance-communityfile-drcn.dbankcdn.com/FileServer/getFile/cmtybbs/422/003/260/2850086000422003260.20220325151505.29540889493637787130144196679369:50530422154009:2800:6C38DAE7D127A85237FA16A44015BE50D2078F687AD6C6B30FAC07077F6B50D7.png\" alt=\"NEP%20%E8%AE%A4%E8%AF%8101