n><span class=\"easyimage easyimage-align-right\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; vertical-align: baseline; border: none; word-break: break-word; background: transparent; outline: 0px; text-align: right; min-width: 10px;\"><img class=\"previewableImage\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: middle; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: 470px; width: 325px;\" src=\"https://alliance-communityfile-drcn.dbankcdn.com/FileServer/getFile/cmtybbs/422/003/260/2850086000422003260.20220325155029.13325749112907192302131753130778:50530422154009:2800:EC90C4A4DD20694D3BE06B2AF298AE02BE717ACCDF6EAD0F921F51EAF9559326.png\" alt=\"8435710ece2d278d444839343debdc8c_900fecc9412e08ad1b18c07f7b4e94d2_8_01.png\" /></span></p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 1em; word-break: break-word; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; clear: both; max-width: 100%; outline: 0px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; word-break: break-word; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bolder;\">HiHopeOS 1.0 RC1 IoT Edition软件发行版OpenHarmony 生态产品兼容性证书</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 1em; word-break: break-word; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; clear: both; max-width: 100%; outline: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 1em; word-break: break-word; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; clear: both; max-width: 100%; outline: 0px;\">HiHopeOS是以OpenHarmony等国产技术为底座的商业发行版，面向不同场景HiHopeOS拥有多个版本，包括支持OpenHarmony轻量设备和小型设备的HiHopeOS IoT Edition （IoT版本）、支持OpenHarmony标准设备的HiHopeOS Standard Edition（标准版）。两个版本基于同一基线的 OpenHarmoy 的不同组件进行研发，两个版本同步演进。早在2021年8月，润和软件已面向金融行业推出业内首个基于OpenHarmony的金融终端发行版（Beta版本），此后将持续推出更多基于HiHopeOS 的行业发行版，如金融发行版、教育发行版、能源发行版等。HiHopeOS核心技术将会逐步开源，并在智慧金融、智慧能源、智慧地产、智慧教育、智慧出行、智慧穿戴、智能家居等领域实现多行业场景落地。</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 1em; word-break: break-word; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; clear: both; max-width: 100%; outline: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 1em; word-break: break-word; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; clear: both; max-width: 100%; outline: 0px;\">目前，国产芯片自给率不足6%，芯片进口约占进口总额18%。同时，全球IoT市场巨大，国产大型IoT操作系统几乎空白，基于OpenHarmony的国产操作系统被寄予厚望。为解决缺&ldquo;芯&rdquo;少&ldquo;魂&rdquo;的行业困境，结合自身在软硬件一体化领域多年的积累，润和软件打造了芯片全栈解决方案平台HiHope，旨在构建一个包含芯片设计与验证、硬件开发生产、硬件测试认证、板级支持软件、芯片调测软件、应用解决方案原型的一站式芯片解决方案平台，致力于打造一个以国产芯片为核心，全面涵盖半导体厂商、模组、板卡、下游客户与场景、综合软硬件服务、开发者的 HiHope 生态圈。</p>', '', 23, ',1,', '原创', '公开', '已发布', '', 0, '', '', 1, 0, '2022-04-23 23:40:41', '2022-04-24 00:02:54');
