previewableImage\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: middle; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\" src=\"https://alliance-communityfile-drcn.dbankcdn.com/FileServer/getFile/cmtybbs/241/148/214/0260086000241148214.20220304105708.67912707157287318859679095634175:50530422154049:2800:BE3AB637BDB957DBED8B9CAD4DEBF8F6F7B2D69071F5D79485200719373B31A1.gif\" alt=\"cke_2499.gif\" /></span>&nbsp;<span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bolder;\">说明：</span>&nbsp;如果本地已有对应的密钥，无需新生成密钥，可以在<span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bolder;\">Generate Key</span>界面中点击下方的Skip跳过密钥生成过程，直接使用已有密钥生成证书请求文件。</p>\n<ul style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 40px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\n<li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\">在Key Store File中，可以点击Choose Existing选择已有的密钥库文件（存储有密钥的.p12文件）；如果没有密钥库文件，点击New进行创建。下面以新创建密钥库文件为例进行说明。&nbsp;<span class=\"easyimage easyimage-full\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: none; word-break: break-word; background: transparent; outline: 0px;\"><img class=\"previewableImage\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: middle; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\" src=\"https://alliance-communityfile-drcn.dbankcdn.com/FileServer/getFile/cmtybbs/241/148/214/0260086000241148214.20220304105708.00766684588536468822817006399754:50530422154049:2800:60B6DAC94F1C844C43ADECCB6242DABED4A1EBAF35287771ADF91334E6211D3F.png\" alt=\"cke_2500.png\" /></span></li>\n<li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\">在Create Key Store窗口中，填写密钥库信息后，点击OK。\n<ul style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 40px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\">\n<li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\">Key Store File：选择密钥库文件存储路径。</li>\n<li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\">Password：设置密钥库密码，必须由大写字母、小写字母、数字和特殊符号中的两种以上字符的组合，长度至少为8位。请记住该密码，后续签名配置需要使用。</li>\n<li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\">Confirm Password：再次输入密钥库密码。</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; word-break: break-word; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span class=\"easyimage easyimage-full\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: none; word-break: break-word; background: transparent; outline: 0px;\"><img class=\"previewableImage\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: middle; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\" src=\"https://alliance-communityfile-drcn.dbankcdn.com/FileServer/getFile/cmtybbs/241/148/214/0260086000241148214.20220304105708.62564020050099821607842804215837:50530422154049:2800:0FF684788A4F253BEF0B8DB6A1040D77D8398FD25EE3BDD446154FBF9CAA9C0D.png\" alt=\"cke_2501.png\" /></span></p>\n<ul style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 40px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\n<li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\">在Generate Key界面中，继续填写密钥信息后，点击Next。\n<ul style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 40px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\">\n<li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\">Alias：密钥的别名信息，用于标识密钥名称。请记住该别名，后续签名配置需要使用。</li>\n<li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\">Password：密钥对应的密码，与密钥库密码保持一致，无需手动输入。</li>\n<li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\">Validity：证书有效期，建议设置为25年及以上，覆盖应用/服务的完整生命周期。</li>\n<li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\">Certificate：输入证书基本信息，如组织、城市或地区、国家码等。</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; word-break: break-word; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span class=\"easyimage easyimage-full\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: none; word-break: break-word; background: transparent; outline: 0px;\"><img class=\"previewableImage\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: middle; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\" src=\"https://alliance-communityfile-drcn.dbankcdn.com/FileServer/getFile/cmtybbs/241/148/214/0260086000241148214.20220304105708.33456343872538473602847436197531:50530422154049:2800:60A775236FD5E97E431561322B813BD1EADF5F99D0979ADFCAA6E679978D6391.png\" alt=\"cke_2502.png\" /></span></p>\n<ul style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 40px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\n<li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\">在Generate CSR界面，选择密钥和设置CSR文件存储路径。&nbsp;<span class=\"easyimage easyimage-full\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: none; word-break: break-word; background: transparent; outline: 0px;\"><img class=\"previewableImage\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: middle; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\" src=\"https://alliance-communityfile-drcn.dbankcdn.com/FileServer/getFile/cmtybbs/241/148/214/0260086000241148214.20220304105708.73591524878336295103983537542908:50530422154049:2800:F0BB6CF44A1962D66A3ED89A86C975E7F674FFBFB98C69275DB566C114BAD265.png\" alt=\"cke_2503.png\" /></span></li>\n<li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\">点击OK按钮，创建CSR文件成功，可以在存储路径下获取生成的密钥库文件（.p12）和证书请求文件（.csr）。&nbsp;<span class=\"easyimage easyimage-full\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: none; word-break: break-word; background: transparent; outline: 0px;\"><img class=\"previewableImage\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: middle; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\" src=\"https://alliance-communityfile-drcn.dbankcdn.com/FileServer/getFile/cmtybbs/241/148/214/0260086000241148214.20220304105708.04719024141410650710816740340271:50530422154049:2800:2E492C33EF3E35633D1CB1FF460C2EBEDFB6160DC0FCDC5245E7A5789996497F.png\" alt=\"cke_2504.png\" /></span>\n<ul style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 40px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\">\n<li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\">\n<ul style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 40px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\">\n<li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\">\n<ol style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 40px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;\">\n<li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\">生成应用证书文件</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; word-break: break-word; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">使用生成密钥和证书请求文件中生成的证书请求文件，来生成应用签名所需的数字证书文件。生成方法如下：</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; word-break: break-word; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">进入DevEco Studio安装目录的<span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bolder;\">Sdk\\toolchains\\lib</span>文件夹下（该SDK目录只能是OpenHarmony SDK，配置方法可参考<a style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; background: 0px 0px transparent; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; transition: color 0.3s ease 0s; color: #0782c1; touch-action: manipulation; text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer;\" href=\"https://gitee.com/openharmony/docs/blob/master/zh-cn/application-dev/quick-start/configuring-openharmony-sdk.md\" rel=\"nofollow\">配置OpenHarmony SDK</a>），打开命令行工具，执行如下命令（如果keytool命令不能执行，请在系统环境变量中添加JDK的环境变量）。其中，只需要修改输入和输出即可快速生成证书文件，即修改**-infile<span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bolder;\">指定证书请求文件csr文件路径，</span>-outfile**指定输出证书文件名及路径。</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; word-break: break-word; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">keytool -gencert -alias \"OpenHarmony Application CA\" -infile myApplication_ohos.csr -outfile myApplication_ohos.cer -keystore OpenHarmony.p12 -sigalg SHA384withECDSA -storepass 123456 -ext KeyUsage:\"critical=digitalSignature\" -validity 3650 -rfc</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; word-break: break-word; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">关于该命令的参数说明如下：</p>\n<ul style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 40px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\n<li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bolder;\">alias</span>：用于签发证书的CA私钥别名，OpenHarmony社区CA私钥存于OpenHarmony.p12密钥库文件中，该参数不能修改。</li>\n<li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bolder;\">infile</span>：证书请求（CSR）文件的路径。</li>\n<li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bolder;\">outfile</span>：输出证书链文件名及路径。</li>\n<li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bolder;\">keystore</span>：签发证书的CA密钥库路径，OpenHarmony密钥库文件名为OpenHarmony.p12，文件在OpenHarmony SDK中<span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bolder;\">Sdk\\toolchains\\lib</span>路径下，该参数不能修改。请注意，该OpenHarmony.p12文件并不是生成密钥和证书请求文件中生成的.p12文件。</li>\n<li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bolder;\">sigalg</span>：证书签名算法，该参数不能修改。</li>\n<li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0p