使用到制作的私钥（.p12）文件、证书（.cer）文件和Profile（.p7b）文件对调试的模块进行签名。</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; word-break: break-word; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">打开<span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bolder;\">File &gt; Project Structure</span>，点击<span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bolder;\">Project &gt; Signing Configs &gt; debug</span>窗口中，去除勾选&ldquo;Automatically generate signing&rdquo;，然后配置指定模块的调试签名信息。</p>\n<ul style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 40px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\n<li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bolder;\">Store File</span>：选择密钥库文件，文件后缀为.p12，该文件为生成密钥和证书请求文件中生成的.p12文件。</li>\n<li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bolder;\">Store Password<