l-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">（我们假设数组参数的长度相同。）</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">以下是使用矢量API的等效矢量计算：</p>\n<pre style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: couriernew, courier, monospace; overflow: auto; white-space: pre-wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; tab-size: 4; color: #2a2b31; background-color: #ffffff; position: relative;\"><code class=\" hljs cs\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 36px 0.5em 0.5em; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-size: 1em; font-family: couriernew, courier, monospace; display: block; background: #f0f0f0; color: black;\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bold; word-break: break-word;\">static</span> final VectorSpecies&lt;Float&gt; SPECIES = FloatVector.SPECIES_PREFERRED;\n\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bold; word-break: break-word;\">void</span> vectorComputation(<span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; 