e=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #008800; word-break: break-word;\">4</span>)\n <span class=\"hljs-number\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #008800; word-break: break-word;\">26.20</span>%  │ │  <span class=\"hljs-number\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #008800; word-break: break-word;\">0</span>x0000000113d438b9: add    <span class=\"hljs-variable\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; word-break: break-word; color: #880000; font-weight: bold;\">$0x8</span>,%ebx\n  <span class=\"hljs-number\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #008800; word-break: break-word;\">6.44</span>%  │ │  <span class=\"hljs-number\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #008800; word-break: break-word;\">0</span>x0000000113d438bc: cmp    %r11d,%ebx\n         \\ │  <span class=\"hljs-number\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #008800; word-break: break-word;\">0</span>x0000000113d438bf: jl     <span class=\"hljs-number\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #008800; word-break: break-word;\">0</span>x0000000113d43890\n</code><button style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 4px 8px 0px; touch-action: manipulation; font-size: 14px; font-family: inherit; line-height: inherit; overflow: visible; appearance: button; position: absolute; cursor: pointer; top: 4px; right: 8px;\">复制</button></pre>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">这是上述代码的JMH微基准的输出，使用Vector API的原型和实现，在向量本质分支Project Panama项目发展储存库。生成的机器码的这些热区域显示了矢量寄存器和矢量指令的清晰转换。我们禁用了循环展开，以使转换更清晰；否则，HotSpot将使用现有的C2循环优化展开此代码。所有Java对象分配都将被取消。</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">在支持谓词寄存器的平台上，上面的示例可以更简单地编写，而无需标量循环来处理尾元素，同时仍可实现最佳性能：</p>\n<pre style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: couriernew, courier, monospace; overflow: auto; white-space: pre-wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; tab-size: 4; color: #2a2b31; background-color: #ffffff; position: relative;\"><code class=\" hljs cs\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 36px 0.5em 0.5em; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-size: 1em; font-family: couriernew, courier, monospace; display: block; background: #f0f0f0; color: black;\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bold; word-break: break-word;\">void</span> vectorComputation(<span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bold; word-break: break-word;\">float</span>[] a, <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bold; word-break: break-word;\">float</span>[] b, <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bold; word-break: break-word;\">float</span>[] c) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bold; word-break: break-word;\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bold; word-break: break-word;\">int</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #008800; word-break: break-word;\">0</span>; i &lt; a.length; i += SPECIES.length()) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-comment\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #888888; word-break: break-word;\">// VectorMask&lt;Float&gt;  m;</span>\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bold; word-break: break-word;\">var</span> m = SPECIES.indexInRange(i, a.length);\n        <span class=\"hljs-comment\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #888888; word-break: break-word;\">// FloatVector va, vb, vc;</span>\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bold; word-break: break-word;\">var</span> va = FloatVector.fromArray(SPECIES, a, i, m);\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bold; word-break: break-word;\">var</span> vb = FloatVector.fromArray(SPECIES, b, i, m);\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bold; word-break: break-word;\">var</span> vc = va.mul(va)\n                   .add(vb.mul(vb))\n                   .neg();\n        vc.intoArray(c, i, m);\n    }\n}\n</code><button style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 4px 8px 0px; touch-action: manipulation; font-size: 14px; font-family: inherit; line-height: inherit; overflow: visible; appearance: button; position: absolute; cursor: pointer; top: 4px; right: 8px;\">复制</button></pre>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">在循环主体中，我们获得了一个循环相关掩码，用于加载和存储操作的输入。当<code style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-size: 1em; font-family: couriernew, courier, monospace;\">i &lt; SPECIES.loopBound(a.length)</code>&nbsp;时，掩码m声明所有通道都已设置。对于循环的最后一次迭代，当<code style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-size: 1em; font-family: couriernew, courier, monospace;\">SPECIES.loopBound(a.length) &lt;= i &lt; a.length and (a.length - i) &lt;= SPECIES.length()</code>时，掩码可以声明未设置通道的后缀。加载和存储操作不会抛出越界异常，因为掩码阻止访问数组长度超出数组长度。</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">我们更希望开发人员为所有受支持的平台以上述风格编写，并实现最佳性能，但今天在没有谓词寄存器的平台上，上述方法并不是最佳的。从理论上讲，C2编译器可以增强以转换循环，剥离最后一次迭代，并从循环主体中删除掩码。这仍然是一个需要进一步调查的领域。</p>\n<h4 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #333333; font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.2; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">运行时编译</h4>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">矢量API有两种实现。第一个在Java中实现操作，因此它是功能性的，但不是最佳的。第二个定义了HotSpot C2运行时编译器的内部矢量操作，以便它可以将矢量计算编译到适当的硬件寄存器和矢量指令（如果可用）。</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">为了避免C2内部函数的爆炸，我们定义了与各种操作相对应的广义内部函数，如一元、二进制、转换等，这些操作采用描述要执行的特定操作的参数。大约20个新的内部特性支持整个API的内部化。</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">我们希望最终将向量类声明为基元类，如Project Valhalla在JEP 401（原始对象）.同时考虑<code style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-size: 1em; font-family: couriernew, courier, monospace;\">Vector&lt;E&gt;</code>及其子类基于值的类，因此应避免对其实例进行身份敏感操作。虽然向量实例抽象地由通道中的元素组成，但这些元素不会被C2标量化-向量的值被视为一个完整的单位，如int或long，映射到适当大小的向量寄存器。C2专门处理矢量实例，以克服逃逸分析中的限制并避免装箱。</p>\n<h4 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #333333; font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.2; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">用于超验操作的英特尔SVML内部特性</h4>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">Vector API 支持浮点矢量上的超越和三角车道操作。在x64上，我们利用 Intel Short Vector Math Library (SVML) 为此类操作提供优化的内部实现。内部运算与java.lang.Math中定义的相应标量运算具有相同的数值属性。</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">SVML操作的程序集源文件位于jdk.incubator.vector模块的源代码中，位于操作系统特定目录下。JDK构建过程将目标操作系统的这些源文件编译为特定于SVML的共享库。这个库相当大，重量不到一兆字节。如果通过jlink构建的JDK映像省略了jdk.incubator.vector模块，则SVML库将不会复制到映像中。</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">目前，该实现仅支持Linux和Windows。我们稍后将考虑macOS支持，因为为程序集源文件提供所需指令是一项非平凡的工作。</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">HotSpot运行时将尝试加载SVML库，如果存在，则将SVML库中的操作绑定到命名的存根例程。C2编译器生成代码，根据操作和向量种类（即元素类型和形状）调用适当的存根例程。</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">在未来，如果Project Panama扩展了对本机调用约定的支持，以支持向量值，然后向量API实现可以从外部源加载SVML库。如果此方法没有性能影响，则不再需要将SVML以源代码形式包含并将其构建到JDK中。在那之前，考虑到潜在的性能提升，我们认为上述方法是可以接受的。</p>\n<h3 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #333333; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.2; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">替代方案</h3>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">HotSpot的自动矢量化是一种替代方法，但它需要大量的工作。此外，与矢量API相比，它仍然是脆弱和有限的，因为具有复杂控制流的自动矢量化非常难以执行。</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">一般来说，即使经过几十年的研究--特别是对于FORTRAN和C数组循环--标量代码的自动矢量化似乎并不是优化临时用户编写循环的可靠策略，除非用户异常仔细地注意未写入的合同关于编译器准备自动矢量化的确切循环。编写一个无法自动矢量化的循环太容易了，原因是人类读者无法检测到的。多年来在自动矢量化方面的工作，即使是在HotSpot，也给我们留下了许多只在特殊场合工作的优化机器。我们想更经常地享受这种机器的使用！</p>\n<h3 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #333333; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.2; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">测试</h3>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">我们将开发组合单元测试，以确保覆盖各种数据集的所有操作、所有支持的类型和形状。</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">我们还将开发性能测试，以确保实现性能目标，并将矢量计算有效地映射到矢量指令。这可能包括JMH微基准，但也需要更现实的有用算法示例。此类测试最初可能驻留在特定于项目的存储库中。考虑到测试的比例和生成测试的方式，在集成到主存储库之前可能需要策展。</p>\n<h3 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #333333; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.2; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">风险和假设</h3>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">API有可能偏向于x64体系结构上支持的SIMD功能，但通过支持AArch64，这种情况可以缓解。这主要适用于显式固定的受支持形状集，这些形状会偏向于以形状通用方式编码算法。我们认为矢量API的大多数其他操作偏向于可移植算法。为了降低这种风险，我们将考虑其他体系结构，特别是ARM标量矢量扩展体系结构，其编程模型动态调整到硬件支持的奇异固定形状。我们欢迎并鼓励在HotSpot ARM特定领域工作的OpenJDK贡献者参与这一努力。</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">矢量API使用框类型（例如，整数）作为基元类型（例如，int）的代理。这一决定是由于Java泛型的当前限制而被迫的，泛型对基元类型怀有敌意。当瓦尔哈拉项目最终引入更有能力的仿制药时，目前的决定将显得尴尬，而且可能需要改变。我们假设，在没有过度向后不兼容的情况下，这种更改是可能的。</p>\n<h3 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #333333; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.2; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">参考引用</h3>\n<ul style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 40px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\n<li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\">更多示例可见《现代Java案例大全》：<a style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; background: 0px 0px transparent; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; transition: color 0.3s ease 0s; color: #0782c1; touch-action: manipulation; text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer;\" href=\"https://github.com/waylau/modern-java-demos\">https://github.com/waylau/modern-java-demos</a></li>\n<li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\">柳伟卫《Java核心编程》：<a style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; background: 0px 0px transparent; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; transition: color 0.3s ease 0s; color: #0782c1; touch-action: manipulation; text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer;\" href=\"https://search.jd.com/Search?keyword=%E6%9F%B3%E4%BC%9F%E5%8D%AB%20Java%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B&amp;amp;enc=utf-8&amp;amp;wq=%E6%9F%B3%E4%BC%9F%E5%8D%AB%20Java%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B&amp;amp;pvid=3f8660921bef4700931a735f536eebfb\">https://search.jd.com/Search?keyword=%E6%9F%B3%E4%BC%9F%E5%8D%AB%20Java%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B&amp;enc=utf-8&amp;wq=%E6%9F%B3%E4%BC%9F%E5%8D%AB%20Java%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B&amp;pvid=3f8660921bef4700931a735f536eebfb</a></li>\n<li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\"><a style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; background: 0px 0px transparent; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; transition: color 0.3s ease 0s; color: #0782c1; touch-action: manipulation; text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer;\" href=\"https://openjdk.java.net/jeps/417\">https://openjdk.java.net/jeps/417</a></li>\n</ul>', '', 14, ',46,', '分享', '公开', '已发布', '推荐', 0, '', '', 1, 0, '2022-04-23 23:44:54', '2022-04-24 00:03:41');
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES (24, 'JDK18已经发布！9大特性之JEP 416：使用方法句柄重新实现核心反射', 3, '', '<h2 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #333333; font-weight: 400; font-size: 24px; line-height: 1.2; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">JEP 416：使用方法句柄重新实现核心反射</h2>\n<h3 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #333333; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.2; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">总结</h3>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">在java.lang.invoke方法句柄的顶部重新实现java.lang.resor.Method、Constructor和Field 。使方法处理反射的底层机制将降低java.lang.reflect 和java.lang.invoke API的维护和开发成本。</p>\n<h3 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #333333; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.2; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">非目标</h3>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">对java.lang.reflect API进行任何更改不是目标。这仅仅是一个实现更改。</p>\n<h3 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #333333; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.2; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">动机</h3>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">核心反射有两种调用方法和构造函数的内部机制。对于快速启动，它使用HotSpot VM中的本机方法来执行特定反射方法或构造函数对象的前几次调用。为了获得更好的峰值性能，在多次调用后，它生成反射操作的字节码，并在后续调用中使用该字节码。</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">对于字段访问，核心反射使用内部的sun.misc.Unsafe API。</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">在Java 7中引入的java.lang.invoke方法处理API中，反射操作共有三种不同的内部机制：</p>\n<ul style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 40px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\n<li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\">虚拟机本机方法，</li>\n<li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\">动态生成的方法字节码存根：<code style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-size: 1em; font-family: couriernew, courier, monospace;\">Method::invoke</code>、<code style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-size: 1em; font-family: couriernew, courier, monospace;\">Constructor::newInstance</code>，以及Unsafe字段的<code style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-size: 1em; font-family: couriernew, courier, monospace;\">Field::get/set</code></li>\n<li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\">方法句柄。</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">当我们更新 java.lang.reflect 和 java.lang.invoke以支持新的语言功能时，例如中设想的那些功能Project Valhalla，我们必须修改所有三个代码路径，这是很昂贵的。此外，当前的实现依赖于VM对生成的字节码的特殊处理，该字节码包装在jdk.internal.reflect.MagicAccessorImpl：</p>\n<ul style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 40px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\n<li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\">可访问性被放宽，以便这些类可以访问其他类的不可访问的字段和方法。</li>\n<li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\">验证被禁用以解决<a style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; background: 0px 0px transparent; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; transition: color 0.3s ease 0s; color: #0782c1; touch-action: manipulation; text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer;\" href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/javase/specs/jls/se16/html/jls-6.html#jls-6.6.2\">JLS第6.6.2节</a>为了支持对对象的Object::clone，以及</li>\n<li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\">行为不端的类加载器用于解决一些安全和兼容性问题。</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #333333; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.2; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">说明</h3>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">通过替换<code style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-size: 1em; font-family: couriernew, courier, monospace;\">Method::invoke</code>、<code style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-size: 1em; font-family: couriernew, courier, monospace;\">Constructor::newInstance</code>，以及Unsafe字段的<code style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-size: 1em; font-family: couriernew, courier, monospace;\">Field::get/set</code>的字节码生成实现，在方法句柄的顶部重新实现java.lang.reflect，作为平台的公共底层反射机制。</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">新实现对特定反射对象的方法句柄执行直接调用。我们仅在虚拟机早期启动期间，在方法手柄机制初始化之前，使用虚拟机的本机反射机制。那就发生在不久之后<code style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-size: 1em; font-family: couriernew, courier, monospace;\">System::initPhase1</code>和之前<code style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-size: 1em; font-family: couriernew, courier, monospace;\">System::initPhase2</code>，之后我们切换到独占使用方法句柄。这个好处Project Loom通过减少本机堆栈帧的使用。</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">为了获得最佳性能，方法、构造函数和字段实例应保存在static final 字段中，以便JIT将它们常量折叠。完成后，微基准显示，新实现的性能明显快于旧实现，提高了43%&ndash;57%。</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">当方法、构造函数和字段实例保存在非常量字段（例如，在非最终字段或数组元素中）中时，微基准显示出一些性能下降。当字段实例不能常量折叠时，字段访问的性能明显比旧实现慢51&ndash;77%。</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">然而，这种降级可能不会对实际应用程序的性能产生太大影响。我们使用真实世界的库运行了几个序列化和反序列化基准测试，发现在</p>\n<ul style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 40px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\n<li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\">自定义JSON序列化和反序列化基准测试，使用Jackson，</li>\n<li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\">XStream转换器类型基准测试，或</li>\n<li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\">Kryo字段序列化器基准测试</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">我们将继续探索提高性能的机会，例如，通过优化字段访问的字节码形状，使具体的MethodHandles 和VarHandles能够由JIT可靠地优化，而不管接收器是否常量。</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">新的实现将降低升级新语言功能的反射支持的成本，并进一步使我们能够通过删除MagicAccessorImpl子类的特殊处理来简化HotSpot VM。</p>\n<h3 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #333333; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.2; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">替代方案</h3>\n<h4 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #333333; font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.2; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">备选方案1：什么都不做</h4>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">保留现有的核心反射实现，以避免任何兼容性风险。为核心反射生成的动态字节码将保留在类文件版本49中，虚拟机将继续特别处理此类字节码。</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">我们拒绝这种选择，因为</p>\n<ul style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 40px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\n<li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\">更新java.lang.reflect 和java.lang.invoke以支持Project Valhalla的原始类和泛型专业化认证的成本将很高，</li>\n<li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\">可能需要VM中的其他特殊规则来支持旧类文件格式限制范围内的新语言功能，以及</li>\n<li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\">Project Loom需要找到一种方法来处理通过核心反射引入本机堆栈帧。</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #333333; font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.2; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">备选方案2：升级到新的字节码库</h4>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">替换核心反射使用的字节码编写器，以使用与类文件格式一起进化的新字节码库，但在其他方面保留现有的核心反射实现，并继续专门处理动态生成的反射字节码。</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">这种替代方案的兼容性风险比我们上面提出的要低，但它仍然是一个相当大的工作量，而且它仍然具有第一种替代方案的第一个和最后一个缺点。</p>\n<h3 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #333333; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.2; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">风险和假设</h3>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">依赖于现有实现的高度特定于实现和未文档化方面的代码可能会受到影响。为了降低此兼容性风险，作为一种解决方法，您可以通过<code style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-size: 1em; font-family: couriernew, courier, monospace;\">-Djdk.reflect.useDirectMethodHandle=false</code>启用旧的实现。</p>\n<ul style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 40px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\n<li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\">检查内部生成的反射类（即，MagicAccessorImpl的子类）的代码将不再工作，必须更新。</li>\n<li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\">方法句柄调用可能比旧的核心反射实现消耗更多的资源。这样的调用涉及调用多个Java方法，以确保在访问之前初始化成员的声明类，因此可能需要更多的堆栈空间来用于必要的执行帧。这可能会导致StackOverflowError，或者，如果在初始化类时引发StackOverflowError，则会导致NoClassDefFoundError。</li>\n<li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\">我们将在未来的版本中删除旧的核心反射实现。<code style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-size: 1em; font-family: couriernew, courier, monospace;\">-Djdk.reflect.useDirectMethodHandle=false</code>解决方法将在该点停止工作。</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #333333; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.2; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">参考引用</h3>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">更多示例可见《Java核心编程》：<a style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; background: 0px 0px transparent; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; transition: color 0.3s ease 0s; color: #0782c1; touch-action: manipulation; text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer;\" href=\"https://github.com/waylau/modern-java-demos\">https://github.com/waylau/modern-java-demos</a></p>', '', 15, ',48,50,54,56,', '行业动态', '公开', '已发布', '推荐', 0, '', '', 1, 0, '2022-04-23 23:45:35', '2022-04-24 00:03:39');
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES (25, 'JDK18已经发布！9大特性之JEP 408：简单Web服务器', 3, '', '<h2 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #333333; font-weight: 400; font-size: 24px; line-height: 1.2; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">JEP 408：简单Web服务器</h2>\n<h3 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #333333; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.2; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">总结</h3>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">提供命令行工具来启动仅提供静态文件的最小Web服务器。没有CGI或类似servlet的功能可用。此工具将有助于原型制作、临时编码和测试目的，特别是在教育环境中。</p>\n<h3 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #333333; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.2; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">目标</h3>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\"> 提供开箱即用的静态HTTP文件服务器，具有易于设置和最低功能。  降低开发者激活能量，让JDK更平易近人。  通过命令行提供默认实现，以及用于编程创建和自定义的小型API。</p>\n<h3 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #333333; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.2; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">非目标</h3>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\"> 提供功能丰富或商业级服务器并不是目标。更好的替代方案以服务器框架（例如Jetty、Netty和Grizzly）和生产服务器（例如Apache Tomcat、Apache httpd和NGINX）的形式存在。这些成熟和性能优化的技术需要努力配置，这正是我们希望避免的。  提供身份验证、访问控制或加密等安全功能不是目标。服务器仅用于测试、开发和调试。因此，它的设计是明确的最小的，以避免与功能齐全的服务器应用程序混淆。</p>\n<h3 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #333333; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.2; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">动机</h3>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">对于开发人员来说，一个常见的成年仪式是在Web上提供一个文件，很可能是一个&ldquo;Hello, world!&rdquo;HTML文件。大多数计算机科学课程向学生介绍Web开发，其中本地测试服务器是常用的。开发人员通常还学习系统管理和Web服务，以及开发工具与基本服务器功能可以派上用场。像这样的教育和非正式任务是需要小型开箱即用服务器的地方。使用案例包括：  Web开发测试，其中使用本地测试服务器模拟客户端-服务器设置。  Web服务或应用程序测试，其中静态文件用作目录结构中的API存根，该目录结构镜像RESTful URL并包含虚拟数据。  跨系统非正式浏览和共享文件，例如，从本地计算机搜索远程服务器上的目录。 当然，在所有这些情况下，我们都可以使用Web服务器框架，但这种方法具有很高的激活能量：我们必须寻找选项，选择一个，下载它，配置它，并在我们能够服务我们的第一个请求之前找出如何使用它。这些步骤相当于相当多的仪式，这是一个缺点；在路上的某个地方卡住可能会令人沮丧，甚至可能会阻碍Java的进一步使用。从命令行或通过几行代码启动的基本Web服务器让我们绕过这个仪式，这样我们就可以专注于手头的任务了。 Python、Ruby、PHP、Erlang和许多其他平台提供开箱即用服务器从命令行运行。这种现有的替代方案表明了对这类工具的公认需求。</p>\n<h3 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #333333; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.2; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">说明</h3>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">简单Web服务器是一个最小的HTTP服务器，用于服务单个目录层次结构。它基于com.sun.net.httpserver包中的Web服务器实现，该软件包自2006年以来一直包含在JDK中。该软件包受到官方支持，我们通过API扩展它，以简化服务器创建和增强请求处理。简单Web服务器可以通过专用的命令行工具jwebserver使用，也可以通过其API以编程方式使用。</p>\n<h4 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #333333; font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.2; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">命令行工具</h4>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">以下命令启动简单Web服务器：</p>\n<pre style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: couriernew, courier, monospace; overflow: auto; white-space: pre-wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; tab-size: 4; color: #2a2b31; background-color: #ffffff; position: relative;\"><code class=\" hljs ruby\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 36px 0.5em 0.5em; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-size: 1em; font-family: couriernew, courier, monospace; display: block; background: #f0f0f0; color: black;\"><span class=\"hljs-variable\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; word-break: break-word;\">$ </span>jwebserver\n</code><button style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 4px 8px 0px; touch-action: manipulation; font-size: 14px; font-family: inherit; line-height: inherit; overflow: visible; appearance: button; position: absolute; cursor: pointer; top: 4px; right: 8px;\">复制</button></pre>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">如果启动成功，则jwebserver将一条消息打印到System.out，列出所服务目录的本地地址和绝对路径。例如：</p>\n<pre style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: couriernew, courier, monospace; overflow: auto; white-space: pre-wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; tab-size: 4; color: #2a2b31; background-color: #ffffff; position: relative;\"><code class=\" hljs coffeescript\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 36px 0.5em 0.5em; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-size: 1em; font-family: couriernew, courier, monospace; display: block; background: #f0f0f0; color: black;\">$ jwebserver\nBinding to loopback <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bold; word-break: break-word;\">by</span> <span class=\"hljs-reserved\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; word-break: break-word;\">default</span>. For all interfaces use <span class=\"hljs-string\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #880000; word-break: break-word;\">\"-b 0.0.0.0\"</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bold; word-break: break-word;\">or</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #880000; word-break: break-word;\">\"-b ::\"</span>.\nServing /cwd <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bold; word-break: break-word;\">and</span> subdirectories <span class=\"hljs-literal\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #008800; word-break: break-word;\">on</span> <span class=\"hljs-number\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #008800; word-break: break-word;\">127.0</span><span class=\"hljs-number\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent