ox-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #008800; word-break: break-word;\">8000</span>/\n</code><button style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 4px 8px 0px; touch-action: manipulation; font-size: 14px; font-family: inherit; line-height: inherit; overflow: visible; appearance: button; position: absolute; cursor: pointer; top: 4px; right: 8px;\">复制</button></pre>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">默认情况下，服务器运行在前台，并绑定环回地址和端口8000。这可以使用-b和-p选项更改。例如，要在端口9000上运行服务器，请使用：</p>\n<pre style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: couriernew, courier, monospace; overflow: auto; white-space: pre-wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; tab-size: 4; color: #2a2b31; background-color: #ffffff; position: relative;\"><code class=\" hljs ruby\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 36px 0.5em 0.5em; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-size: 1em; font-family: couriernew, courier, monospace; display: block; background: #f0f0f0; color: black;\"><span class=\"hljs-variable\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; word-break: break-word;\">$ </span>jwebserver -p <span class=\"hljs-number\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #008800; word-break: break-word;\">9000</span>\n</code><button