webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bold; word-break: break-word;\">interface</span> Request {\n    URI getRequestURI();\n    String getRequestMethod();\n    Headers getRequestHeaders();\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bold; word-break: break-word;\">default</span> Request with(String headerName, List&lt;String&gt; headerValues)\n    {...}\n}\n</code><button style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 4px 8px 0px; touch-action: manipulation; font-size: 14px; font-family: inherit; line-height: inherit; overflow: visible; appearance: button; position: absolute; cursor: pointer; top: 4px; right: 8px;\">复制</button></pre>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">我们引入了一个更简单的请求接口，以提供不可变请求状态的有限视图：</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">这可以直接自定义现有处理程序，例如：</p>\n<pre style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: couriernew, courier, monospace; overflow: auto; white-space: pre-wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; tab-size: 4; color: #2a2b31; background-color: #ffffff; position: relative;\"><code class=\" hljs coffeescript\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 36px 0.5em 0.5em; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-size: 1em; font-family: couriernew, courier, monospace; display: block; background: #f0f0f0; color: black;\">jshell&gt; <span class=\"hljs-reserved\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; word-break: break-word;\">var</span> h = HttpHandlers.handleOrElse(r<span class=\"hljs-function\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; word-break: break-word;\"> -&gt;</span> r.getRequestMethod().equals(<span class=\"hljs-string\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #880000; word-break: break-word;\">\"PUT\"</span>),\n   ...&gt; <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bold; word-break: break-word;\">new</span> SomePutHandler(), <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bold; word-break: break-word;\">new</span> SomeHandler());\njshell&gt; <span class=\"hljs-reserved\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; word-break: break-word;\">var</span> f = Filter.adaptRequest(<span class=\"hljs-string\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #880000; word-break: break-word;\">\"Add Foo header\"</span>, r<span class=\"hljs-function\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; word-break: break-word;\"> -&gt;</span> r.<span class=\"hljs-reserved\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; word-break: break-word;\">with</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #880000; word-break: break-word;\">\"Foo\"</span>, List.<span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bold; word-break: break-word;\">of</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #880000; word-break: break-word;\">\"Bar\"</span>)));\njshell&gt; <span class=\"hljs-reserved\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; word-break: break-word;\">var</span> s = HttpServer.create(<span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bold; word-break: break-word;\">new</span> InetSocketAddress(<span class=\"hljs-number\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #008800; word-break: break-word;\">8080</span>),\n   ...&gt; <span class=\"hljs-number\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #008800; word-break: break-word;\">10</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #880000; word-break: break-word;\">\"/\"</span>, h, f);\njshell&gt; s.start();\n</code><button style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 4px 8px 0px; touch-action: manipulation; font-size: 14px; font-family: inherit; line-height: inherit; overflow: visible; appearance: button; position: absolute; cursor: pointer; top: 4px; right: 8px;\">复制</button></pre>\n<h4 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #333333; font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.2; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">替代方案</h4>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">我们考虑了命令行工具的替代方案：  java -m jdk.httpserver：最初，简单Web服务器是使用java -m jdk.httpserver命令运行的，而不是使用专用的命令行工具运行的。虽然这仍然是可能的（事实上，jwebserver在引擎盖下使用java -m ...命令），但我们决定引入一个专用工具来提高便利性和平易近人。 我们在原型开发过程中考虑了几种API替代方案：  一个新的类DeleatingHandler-将自定义方法捆绑在一个单独的类中，该类实现了HttpHandler接口。我们放弃了此选项，因为它是以引入新类型而不添加更多功能为代价的。这种新类型也很难发现。另一方面，HttpHandlers类使用外板模式，其中类的静态帮助器方法或工厂捆绑在新类中。几乎相同的名称使查找类变得容易，便于理解和使用新的API点，并隐藏委托的实现细节。  HttpHandler即服务-将HttpHandler转换为服务，并提供内部文件服务器处理程序实现。开发人员可以提供自定义处理程序，也可以使用默认提供程序。这种方法的缺点是，它更难使用，而且对于我们希望提供的小功能集来说，它相当复杂。 Filter 而不是HttpHandler-仅使用过滤器，而不是处理程序来处理请求。过滤器通常是预处理或后处理，这意味着它们在调用处理程序之前或之后访问请求，例如用于身份验证或日志记录。但是，它们并不是为了完全取代处理程序而设计的。以这种方式使用它们将是违反直觉的，方法也将更难找到。</p>\n<h2 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #333333; font-weight: 400; font-size: 24px; line-height: 1.2; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">参考引用</h2>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">更多示例可见《Java核心编程》：<a style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; background: 0px 0px transparent; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; transition: color 0.3s ease 0s; color: #0782c1; touch-action: manipulation; text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer;\" href=\"https://github.com/waylau/modern-java-demos\">https://github.com/waylau/modern-java-demos</a></p>', '', 27, ',47,49,53,55,', '行业动态', '公开', '已发布', '推荐', 0, '', '', 1, 0, '2022-04-23 23:46:24', '2022-04-24 00:03:38');
