ca, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">我们将原本复杂业务逻辑关进了容器，数据在容器（函子）里做各种转换，即使存在学生信息缺失的情况我们也不用担心NPE，因为Maybe函子自身的特性已经将这种东西消化掉了。</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; word-break: break-word; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; word-break: break-word; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; word-break: break-word; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">2、向第一个学生打招呼，并招呼语以&ldquo;!&nbsp;&rdquo;结束，然后把名称大写。</p>\n<pre class=\" hljs javascript\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0.5em; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: couriernew, courier, monospace; overflow: auto; background: #2b2b2b; color: #a9b7c6; white-space: pre-wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; tab-size: 4; min-height: 25px; position: relative;\">Maybe&lt;Student&gt; boxedFirstStudent = R.safeFirst(students);\n\n<span class=\"hljs-built_in\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bold; word-break: break-word;\">Function</span>&lt;Student, Maybe&lt;<span class=\"hljs-built_in\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bold; word-break: break-word;\">String</span>&gt;&gt; safeNameOf\n        = target -&gt; R.prop(target, <span class=\"hljs-string\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #880000; word-break: break-word;\">\"name\"</span>, <span class=\"hljs-built_in\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bold; word-break: break-word;\">String</span>.class);\n<span class=\"hljs-built_in\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bold; word-break: break-word;\">Function</span>&lt;<span class=\"hljs-built_in\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bold; word-break: break-word;\">String</span>, <span class=\"hljs-built_in\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bold; word-break: break-word;\">String</span>&gt; upper\n        = s -&gt; s.toUpperCase();\n<span class=\"hljs-built_in\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bold; word-break: break-word;\">Function</span>&lt;<span class=\"hljs-built_in\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bold; word-break: break-word;\">String</span>, <span class=\"hljs-built_in\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bold; word-break: break-word;\">String</span>&gt; greet\n        = name -&gt; name + <span class=\"hljs-string\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #880000; word-break: break-word;\">\", hello my friend!\"</span>;\n\nMaybe&lt;<span class=\"hljs-built_in\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bold; word-break: break-word;\">String</span>&gt; safeName = R.flatMap(safeNameOf, boxedFirstStudent);\nMaybe&lt;<span class=\"hljs-built_in\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bold; word-break: break-word;\">String</span>&gt; boxedGreeting = R.map(R.compose(upper, greet), safeName);\n\n<span class=\"hljs-built_in\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bold; word-break: break-word;\">String</span> greeting = boxedGreeting.orElseGet(<span class=\"hljs-literal\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #008800; word-break: break-word;\">null</span>);\nSystem.out.println(greeting);</pre>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; word-break: break-word; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; word-break: break-word; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; word-break: break-word; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">我们同样可以得到下面的结果。</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; word-break: break-word; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; word-break: break-word; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; word-break: break-word; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">但是我们在代码中没有看到丑陋的数据处理逻辑，而且即使存在名称确实的情况，我们代码中也不会出现NPE。</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; word-break: break-word; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; word-break: break-word; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; word-break: break-word; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">这些函数可以随意组合，像搭积木一样，构建更加复杂的业务，只要你想就可以做到，拷贝上面的代码，你可以本地尝试运行。</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; word-break: break-word; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; word-break: break-word; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; word-break: break-word; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">祝大家都写出好代码。：)</p>', '', 29, ',39,37,36,43,44,', '改进意见', '公开', '已发布', '', 0, 'Hot', '', 1, 0, '2022-04-23 23:51:02', '2022-04-24 00:03:33');
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES (29, 'Redis客户端Jedis、Lettuce 和 Redisson优缺点总结', 3, '', '<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; word-break: break-word; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Redis 官方推荐的 Java 客户端有Jedis、Lettuce 和 Redisson。本文总结这些客服端的优缺点</p>\n<h1 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #333333; font-weight: 400; font-size: 28px; line-height: 1.2; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">1. Jedis</h1>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; word-break: break-word; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Jedis 是老牌的 Redis 的 Java 实现客户端，提供了比较全面的 Redis 命令的支持，其官方网址是：https://github.com/redis/jedis</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; word-break: break-word; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">优点：</p>\n<ul style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 40px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\n<li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\">支持全面的 Redis 操作特性（可以理解为API比较全面）。</li>\n<li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\">老牌的redis客户端，使用很稳定; spring-boot 1.x 默认使用jedis;</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; word-break: break-word; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">缺点：</p>\n<ul style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 40px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\n<li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\">使用阻塞的 IO，且其方法调用都是同步的，程序流需要等到 sockets 处理完 IO 才能执行，不支持异步；</li>\n<li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\">Jedis 客户端实例不是线程安全的，所以需要通过连接池来使用 Jedis。</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #333333; font-weight: 400; font-size: 28px; line-height: 1.2; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">2. Lettuce</h1>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; word-break: break-word; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Lettuce是一种可扩展的线程安全的 Redis 客户端，支持异步模式。如果避免阻塞和事务操作，如BLPOP和MULTIEXEC，多个线程就可以共享一个连接。Lettuce 底层基于 Netty，支持高级的 Redis 特性，比如哨兵，集群，管道，自动重新连接和Redis数据模型。Lettuce 的官网地址是：https://github.com/lettuce-io/lettuce-core</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; word-break: break-word; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">优点：</p>\n<ul style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 40px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\n<li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\">支持同步异步通信模式；</li>\n<li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\">Lettuce 的 API 是线程安全的，如果不是执行阻塞和事务操作，如BLPOP和MULTIEXEC，多个线程就可以共享一个连接；</li>\n<li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\">spring-boot 2.x 默认使用Lettuce;</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #333333; font-weight: 400; font-size: 28px; line-height: 1.2; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">3. Redisson</h1>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; word-break: break-word; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Redisson 是一个在 Redis 的基础上实现的 Java 驻内存数据网格（In-Memory Data Grid）。它不仅提供了一系列的分布式的 Java 常用对象，还提供了许多分布式服务。其中包括( BitSet, Set, Multimap, SortedSet, Map, List, Queue, BlockingQueue, Deque, BlockingDeque, Semaphore, Lock, AtomicLong, CountDownLatch, Publish / Subscribe, Bloom filter, Remote service, Spring cache, Executor service, Live Object service, Scheduler service) Redisson 提供了使用Redis 的最简单和最便捷的方法。Redisson 的宗旨是促进使用者对Redis的关注分离（Separation of Concern），从而让使用者能够将精力更集中地放在处理业务逻辑上。Redisson的官方网址是：https://redisson.org/</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; word-break: break-word; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">优点：</p>\n<ul style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 40px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\n<li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\">使用者对 Redis 的关注分离，可以类比 Spring 框架，这些框架搭建了应用程序的基础框架和功能，提升开发效率，让开发者有更多的时间来关注业务逻辑；</li>\n<li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\">提供很多分布式相关操作服务，例如，分布式锁，分布式集合，可通过Redis支持延迟队列等。</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; word-break: break-word; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">缺点：</p>\n<ul style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 40px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\n<li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\">Redisson 对字符串的操作支持比较差。</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #333333; font-weight: 400; font-size: 28px; line-height: 1.2; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">4. 使用建议</h1>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; word-break: break-word; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">一般是采用如下搭配组合。</p>\n<ul style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 40px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\n<li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\">Jedis + Redisson</li>\n<li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\">Lettuce + Redisson</li>\n</ul>', '', 16, ',36,37,38,45,', '翻译', '公开', '已发布', '精华', 0, '', '', 1, 0, '2022-04-23 23:51:47', '2022-04-24 00:03:44');
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES (30, '【Ehcache开发指南】004：Ehcache基础——XML配置详解', 3, '', '<h1 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #333333; font-weight: 400; font-size: 28px; line-height: 1.2; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">XML配置详解</h1>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">在创建时配置CacheManager可以使用XML文件。</p>\n<h2 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #333333; font-weight: 400; font-size: 24px; line-height: 1.2; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\">XML元素</h2>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">XML文件的schema定义，详见<a style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; background: 0px 0px transparent; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; transition: color 0.3s ease 0s; color: #0782c1; touch-action: manipulation; text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer;\" href=\"https://www.ehcache.org/documentation/3.9/xsds.html#core\">https://www.ehcache.org/documentation/3.9/xsds.html#core</a></p>\n<h3 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #333333; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.2; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\"><code style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-size: 1em; font-family: couriernew, courier, monospace;\">&lt;config&gt;</code>根元素</h3>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">XML文件中的一个<code style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-size: 1em; font-family: couriernew, courier, monospace;\">&lt;config&gt;</code>元素提供CacheManager的定义。</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bolder;\">注</span>：Ehcache允许使用相同的XML配置文件创建多个CacheManager实例。与JSR-107 javax.cache.spi.CachingProvider相比，Ehcache不维护CacheManager实例的注册表。</p>\n<h3 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #333333; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.2; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\"><code style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-size: 1em; font-family: couriernew, courier, monospace;\">&lt;service&gt;</code>元素</h3>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\"><code style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-size: 1em; font-family: couriernew, courier, monospace;\">&lt;service&gt;</code>元素是用于指定CacheManager管理的服务的扩展点。</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">以这种方式定义的每个Service都以与CacheManager相同的生命周期管理。对于为CacheManager定义的每个Service ，在CacheManager.init处理期间调用Service.start，在CacheManager.close 处理期间调用Service.stop方法。</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">然后，这些Service实例可以被CacheManager管理的Cache实例使用。</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">JSR-107使用XML配置（以及Ehcache 3的模块化体系结构）的此扩展点，如JSR-107配置部分.</p>\n<h3 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #333333; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.2; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\"><code style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-size: 1em; font-family: couriernew, courier, monospace;\">&lt;default-serializers&gt;</code>元素</h3>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\"><code style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-size: 1em; font-family: couriernew, courier, monospace;\">&lt;default-serializers&gt;</code>元素表示在CacheManager级别配置的Serializers。它是<code style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-size: 1em; font-family: couriernew, courier, monospace;\">&lt;serializer&gt;</code>元素的集合，需要Serializer的type和完全限定的类名。</p>\n<h3 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #333333; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.2; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\"><code style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-size: 1em; font-family: couriernew, courier, monospace;\">&lt;default-copiers&gt;</code>元素</h3>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\"><code style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-size: 1em; font-family: couriernew, courier, monospace;\">&lt;default-copiers&gt;</code>元素表示在CacheManager级别配置的Copiers 。它是<code style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-size: 1em; font-family: couriernew, courier, monospace;\">&lt;copier&gt;</code>元素的集合，需要Copier的type和完全限定的类名。</p>\n<h3 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #333333; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.2; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\"><code style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-size: 1em; font-family: couriernew, courier, monospace;\">&lt;persistence&gt;</code>元素</h3>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\"><code style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-size: 1em; font-family: couriernew, courier, monospace;\">&lt;persistence&gt;</code>元素表示Persistence，在创建PersistentCacheManager时使用。它需要在磁盘上存储数据的directory位置。</p>\n<h3 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; color: #333333; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.2; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; background-color: #ffffff;\"><code style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-size: 1em; font-family: couriernew, courier, monospace;\">&lt;cache&gt;</code>元素</h3>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\"><code style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-size: 1em; font-family: couriernew, courier, monospace;\">&lt;cache&gt;</code>元素表示将由CacheManager创建和管理的Cache实例。每个<code style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-size: 1em; font-family: couriernew, courier, monospace;\">&lt;cache&gt;</code>都需要alias属性，在运行时使用<code style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-size: 1em; font-family: couriernew, courier, monospace;\">org.ehcache.CacheManager.getCache(String, Class&lt;K&gt;, Class&lt;V&gt;)</code>方法检索相应的<code style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-size: 1em; font-family: couriernew, courier, monospace;\">Cache&lt;K, V&gt;</code>实例。可选的使用uses-template允许引用<code style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-size: 1em; font-family: couriernew, courier, monospace;\">&lt;cache-template&gt;</code>元素的name属性。</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">以下所支持的嵌套元素是可选的：</p>\n<ul style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 40px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\n<li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; list-style: disc;\"><code style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-size: 1em; font-family: couriernew, courier, monospace;\">&lt;key-type&gt;</code>：<code style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-size: 1em; font-famil