INSERT INTO `article` VALUES (33, '教您如何精准召回卸载用户', 3, '', '<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\"><img class=\"previewableImage\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: middle; border: 0px; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://alliance-communityfile-drcn.dbankcdn.com/FileServer/getFile/cmtybbs/303/188/248/0070086200303188248.20220411102620.55207017213051876069456932840470:50530422155539:2800:BF93A48B72750266D86CD68AE6F94634134FFEE28EA5F776CB7445899CF00D2B.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">当用户卸载App彻底流失时，应用内消息等便捷的用户触达交互纽带将无法再次连通他们，且对于卸载用户的判定更是技术瓶颈。如何便捷且合理的通过运营策略将卸载用户召回，是用户运营同学迫切想知道的答案。&nbsp;<img class=\"previewableImage\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: middle; border: 0px; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://alliance-communityfile-drcn.dbankcdn.com/FileServer/getFile/cmtybbs/303/188/248/0070086200303188248.20220411102631.21440654977571724894144791823293:50530422155539:2800:86D6A4BA51F4DB68E952D87E563276E17401E23042A24241BD47CAC12377F0B3.png\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;<img class=\"previewableImage\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: middle; border: 0px; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://alliance-communityfile-drcn.dbankcdn.com/FileServer/getFile/cmtybbs/303/188/248/0070086200303188248.20220411102639.07721069946593498516988678195403:50530422155539:2800:9AFBF40DE9797C1447C4D71EFC605F5C7C8F0B79DFE8C0C00DF1DBDF61C9F908.png\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;<img class=\"previewableImage\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: middle; border: 0px; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://alliance-communityfile-drcn.dbankcdn.com/FileServer/getFile/cmtybbs/303/188/248/0070086200303188248.20220411102647.67513383666893184842932121367336:50530422155539:2800:21AB141249A64F52855552D5879946FCDA3CD176A95934B5A366BE64B5600684.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">某知名RPG游戏对玩家的活跃度要求极高，通常会判定超过3天未登录的用户可能已彻底卸载。对于卸载用户的召回，运营同学以<span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; font-weight: bolder;\">华为分析+应用市场</span>礼包活动的全新尝试有了新的突破。&nbsp;<img class=\"previewableImage\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: middle; border: 0px; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://alliance-communityfile-drcn.dbankcdn.com/FileServer/getFile/cmtybbs/303/188/248/0070086200303188248.20220411102712.78354385604352543609297311642423:50530422155539:2800:4789521071F376E88EFBD1FF44D3B7F37C3913FC1E43499F7299D089D8222C98.png\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;本次活动共触达3w近14天卸载用户，共有6k+用户被成功召回，**召回率达18.41%。其中付费用户占比11.04%**。（效果数据真实，由客户提供）&nbsp;<img class=\"previewableImage\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: middle; border: 0px; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://alliance-communityfile-drcn.dbankcdn.com/FileServer/getFile/cmtybbs/303/188/248/0070086200303188248.20220411102721.29107901580547030368811665427036:50530422155539:2800:8A9255BE9932CA403FA8D7526572254C2F5F70583A6499C85656B0E2B4B7C11D.png\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;<img class=\"previewableImage\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: middle; border: 0px; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://alliance-communityfile-drcn.dbankcdn.com/FileServer/getFile/cmtybbs/303/188/248/0070086200303188248.20220411102727.24399162199850890986486961339227:50530422155539:2800:0A0B0B52B714A8C60B54C8EFEDD1C9D4B5D3F6E45003920E879B31A7DCDE7265.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">1.结合华为分析的AI预测模型，圈定特定目标用户，例如高概率流失、付费人群，您可针对不同受众群组开展精细化运营活动。</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">2.由华为分析提供的用户生命周期模型可按照用户使用App的深度，将用户分为新手期、成长期、成熟期、沉默期、流失期，可 针对不同生命周期阶段人群制定差异化运营策略。</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">3.基于用户标签和用户事件通过华为分析灵活创建目标受众，结合行为特征洞察，开展差异化、针对性运营。&nbsp;<img class=\"previewableImage\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: middle; border: 0px; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://alliance-communityfile-drcn.dbankcdn.com/FileServer/getFile/cmtybbs/303/188/248/0070086200303188248.20220411102808.61187017491774111309407046092798:50530422155539:2800:D81733B53FB858BB3CD393A674787D048DA07F206C5CF8ECFCE8DE9FC4F8E83C.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff; word-break: break-word !important;\">欲了解卸载召回场景的详细操作流程，可参考资料说明。更多关于<a style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; background: 0px 0px transparent; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; transition: color 0.3s ease 0s; color: #0782c1; touch-action: manipulation; text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer;\" href=\"https://developer.huawei.com/consumer/cn/doc/development/HMSCore-Guides/introduction-0000001050745149?ha_source=hms1\">华为分析服务</a>的相关介绍，请访问<a style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; background: 0px 0px transparent; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; transition: color 0.3s ease 0s; color: #0782c1; touch-action: manipulation; text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer;\" href=\"https://developer.huawei.com/consumer/cn/hms?ha_source=hms1\">华为开发者联盟官网</a>，期待为您打造更好更快的数据运营体验。</p>\n<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; min-height: 28.8px; color: #2a2b31; font-family: PingFangSC-Regular, \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-ser